1
00:00:00,300 --> 00:00:01,367
So this whole collaboration...

2
00:00:01,368 --> 00:00:02,669
was all your doing?

3
00:00:04,904 --> 00:00:06,373
Who do I think I am?

4
00:00:06,940 --> 00:00:08,875
How could I ever be good enough for you?

5
00:00:09,943 --> 00:00:11,444
Am I doing okay so far?

6
00:00:17,183 --> 00:00:18,218
It's not like that.

7
00:00:18,618 --> 00:00:19,753
Then what is it?

8
00:00:21,988 --> 00:00:23,089
It's just work.

9
00:00:23,623 --> 00:00:24,691
I know.

10
00:00:25,892 --> 00:00:27,594
I was such a fool.

11
00:00:28,762 --> 00:00:30,430
I confused work with real life...

12
00:00:31,765 --> 00:00:33,967
and actually thought we were friends.

13
00:00:43,943 --> 00:00:44,644
Just listen to me.

14
00:00:44,644 --> 00:00:45,644
Enough.

15
00:00:47,881 --> 00:00:49,014
This "immersive experience"...

16
00:00:49,015 --> 00:00:50,417
I've definitely gotten the message.

17
00:00:51,117 --> 00:00:52,852
Thanks for the lesson, Mr. Hei.

18
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:55,360
I take back what I said...

19
00:00:55,855 --> 00:00:58,524
about us being more
than just A-You and Youzhi,

20
00:00:58,525 --> 00:01:00,126
and all that "Black and White" talk.

21
00:01:01,594 --> 00:01:02,694
From now on,

22
00:01:02,695 --> 00:01:04,664
let's just stick to our roles.

23
00:01:05,031 --> 00:01:06,031
As for me,

24
00:01:06,533 --> 00:01:08,635
I'll play along with the promo

25
00:01:09,335 --> 00:01:11,371
so you can get your fame and fortune.

26
00:01:19,012 --> 00:01:20,647
Do you think I'm that easy to fool?

27
00:01:21,815 --> 00:01:23,115
That a few simple moves

28
00:01:23,116 --> 00:01:24,517
are all it takes to get a reaction?

29
00:01:26,653 --> 00:01:28,054
I guess it's true.

30
00:01:29,255 --> 00:01:30,557
Like I said before,

31
00:01:31,224 --> 00:01:32,425
you're a real pro.

32
00:01:34,594 --> 00:01:36,629
I'm the one who got too caught up in it.

33
00:01:39,866 --> 00:01:41,334
There are no cameras now.

34
00:01:41,801 --> 00:01:43,235
We're not filming.

35
00:01:43,236 --> 00:01:44,756
This has nothing to do with publicity.
